                <h1>機會</h1>
<p>貝林資科院的教育不只是唸書</p>            
            </div>

            <div id="col1">

                <ul class="side-nav">
	<li><a href="/prospective/zh-tw/opportunities/applied-learning/" class="">應用所學</a></li>
